20 SUMMARY
2211 This amendment, which is the majority report of the committee, establishes a start date
2222 for the Maine State Board for Licensure of Architects, Landscape Architects and Interior
2233 Designers to begin requiring continuing education prerequisites for the renewal of architect
2244 licenses. It also removes the exemption from continuing education requirements for a
2255 retired licensed architect.
